    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Some info about how Geth handles it:\r\n\r\n* Txs within a block are sorted by `effectiveMinerFee`, which is `Math.min(tx.maxPriorityFeePerGas, tx.maxFeePerGas - block.header.baseFeePerGas)`\r\n\r\n* If a tx is of type `0x0` or `0x1`, then we use `tx.gasPrice` instead of `tx.maxPriorityFeePerGas` and `tx.maxFeePerGas`\r\n\r\n",
